    "difficulty": 3,
    "stem": "A sector of a circle with radius 9 has an area of \\(27\\pi\\). What is the central angle of the sector, in degrees?",
    "answer": 120,
    "solutionStandard": "\\(\\dfrac{\\theta}{360}\\times\\pi(9)^2 = 27\\pi\\), so \\(\\dfrac{\\theta}{360}\\times81=27\\), giving \\(\\theta/360=1/3\\), so \\(\\theta=120\\).",
    "timeTargetSec": 70
  },
